0 0 0 12 0V2Z\"></path></svg></div><p class=\"text-gray-300 mt-4\">Troféu de Campeão + Premiação</p></div></div><div class=\"absolute -inset-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-gold/20 via-gold/40 to-gold/20 rounded-2xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 blur-sm -z-10\"></div></div><div class=\"relative group glass-gold glass-hover glass-shine rounded-2xl overflow-hidden \" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/10 via-transparent to-transparent opacity-50 rounded-2xl pointer-events-none\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 h-full\"><div class=\"p-6\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gold mb-4 text-center\">MVP do Campeonato</h3><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"flex items-center\"><div class=\"bg-gold/20 p-3 rounded-full mr-4 flex items-center justify-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-award text-gold h-10 w-10\"><path d=\"m15.477 12.89 1.515 8.526a.5.5 0 0 1-.81.47l-3.58-2.687a1 1 0 0 0-1.197 0l-3.586 2.686a.5.5 0 0 1-.81-.469l1.514-8.526\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"8\" r=\"6\"></circle></svg></div><div><p class=\"text-white\">Jogador mais valioso</p><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-400\">Troféu + Skin no valor de</p></div></div><div class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gold\">R$ 250,00</div></div></div></div><div class=\"absolute -inset-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-gold/20 via-gold/40 to-gold/20 rounded-2xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 blur-sm -z-10\"></div></div></div><div class=\"text-center mt-10\"><a class=\"inline-block bg-gold/10 text-gold font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-md hover:bg-gold/20 transition-colors border border-gold/30\" href=\"/premiacao\">Ver detalhes completos da premiação</a></div></div></section><section class=\"py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-black via-gray-900 to-black\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-16\"><div class=\"space-y-4 mb-12 text-center\"><div class=\"inline-block bg-gold/20 backdrop-blur-sm px-4 py-2 rounded-full\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><span class=\"text-gold font-semibold\">Parceria</span></div><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gold\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">Seja um Patrocinador</h2></div><div class=\"text-center\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"relative group glass-gold glass-hover glass-shine rounded-2xl overflow-hidden \" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/10 via-transparent to-transparent opacity-50 rounded-2xl pointer-events-none\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 h-full\"><div class=\"p-8\"><p class=\"text-white text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6\">O <span class=\"text-gold font-bold\">Querido Camp</span> é um campeonato que movimenta o cenário de CS2 em Sergipe, conectando jogadores, criadores de conteúdo e marcas que acreditam no potencial dos eSports.</p><p class=\"text-white text-lg leading-relaxed\">Nosso objetivo é <span class=\"text-gold font-bold\">profissionalizar e dar visibilidade</span> ao cenário local, oferecendo às marcas exposição direta a um público jovem e engajado.</p></div></div><div class=\"absolute -inset-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-gold/20 via-gold/40 to-gold/20 rounded-2xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 blur-sm -z-10\"></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mb-12\"><h3 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12\"><span class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-gold to-orange bg-clip-text text-transparent\">Planos de Patrocínio</span></h3></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6\"><div class=\"h-full\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"relative h-full bg-gradient-